data.description: Look no further, this is your chance to get into this highly sought-after part of Grant Park! This home comes complete with not just one, but TWO fully renovated 3 bed 2 bath units. They both are identical and come complete with granite in the kitchen, and hardwood floors throughout, and each has its own private entrance as well as plenty of parking in the back. Zoned Commercial and Nestled 5 minutes to the Beltline and THE BEACON -Grant Park's new trendy and lively Food Hall. This property presents an extensive amount of income-producing opportunities. Here are a few- Buy and Hold, Duplex style- lease out both units, or just one and live in one, tear down and create open space for more commercial opportunities in Grant park
